     fhir:Narrative.div "<div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"><p class=\"res-header-id\"><b>Generated Narrative: ValueSet IMMZD2DTMumpsVS</b></p><a name=\"IMMZD2DTMumpsVS\"> </a><a name=\"hcIMMZD2DTMumpsVS\"> </a><p>This value set expansion contains 12 concepts.</p><table class=\"codes\"><tr><td><b>System</b></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\"><b>Code</b></td><td><b>Display</b></td><td><b>Definition</b></td></tr><tr><td><a name=\"IMMZD2DTMumpsVS-http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK-Client's|20age|20is|20less|20than|2012|20months-42\"> </a><code>http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK</code></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZDAK.html#IMMZDAK-Client.39sageislessthan12months-42\">Client's age is less than 12 months-42</a></td><td>Client's age is less than 12 months</td><td><div><p>Today's date − \"Date of birth\" &lt; 12 months</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><a name=\"IMMZD2DTMumpsVS-http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK-Client|20is|20not|20due|20for|20mumps|20vaccination-48\"> </a><code>http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK</code></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZDAK.html#IMMZDAK-Clientisnotdueformumpsvaccination-48\">Client is not due for mumps vaccination-48</a></td><td>Client is not due for mumps vaccination</td><td><div><p>\"Immunization recommendation status\" = \"Not due\"</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><a name=\"IMMZD2DTMumpsVS-http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK-No|20mumps|20primary|20series|20doses|20were|20administered-125\"> </a><code>http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK</code></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZDAK.html#IMMZDAK-Nomumpsprimaryseriesdoseswereadministered-125\">No mumps primary series doses were administered-125</a></td><td>No mumps primary series doses were administered</td><td><div><p>Count of vaccines administered (where \"Vaccine type\" = \"Mumps-containing vaccines\" and \"Type of dose\" = \"Primary series\") = 0</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><a name=\"IMMZD2DTMumpsVS-http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK-Client's|20age|20is|20more|20than|20or|20equal|20to|2012|20months-42\"> </a><code>http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK</code></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZDAK.html#IMMZDAK-Client.39sageismorethanorequalto12months-42\">Client's age is more than or equal to 12 months-42</a></td><td>Client's age is more than or equal to 12 months</td><td><div><p>Today's date − \"Date of birth\" ≥ 12 months</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><a name=\"IMMZD2DTMumpsVS-http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK-Live|20vaccine|20was|20administered|20in|20the|20past|204|20weeks-92\"> </a><code>http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK</code></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZDAK.html#IMMZDAK-Livevaccinewasadministeredinthepast4weeks-92\">Live vaccine was administered in the past 4 weeks-92</a></td><td>Live vaccine was administered in the past 4 weeks</td><td><div><p>Today's date − latest \"Date and time of vaccination\" (where \"Live vaccine\" = TRUE) &lt; 4 weeks</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><a name=\"IMMZD2DTMumpsVS-http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK-No|20live|20vaccine|20was|20administered|20in|20the|20past|204|20weeks-92\"> </a><code>http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK</code></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZDAK.html#IMMZDAK-Nolivevaccinewasadministeredinthepast4weeks-92\">No live vaccine was administered in the past 4 weeks-92</a></td><td>No live vaccine was administered in the past 4 weeks</td><td><div><p>Today's date − latest \"Date and time of vaccination\" (where \"Live vaccine\" = TRUE) ≥ 4 weeks</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><a name=\"IMMZD2DTMumpsVS-http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK-Client|20is|20due|20for|20mumps|20vaccination-44\"> </a><code>http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK</code></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZDAK.html#IMMZDAK-Clientisdueformumpsvaccination-44\">Client is due for mumps vaccination-44</a></td><td>Client is due for mumps vaccination</td><td><div><p>\"Immunization recommendation status\" = \"Due\"</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><a name=\"IMMZD2DTMumpsVS-http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK-One|20mumps|20primary|20series|20dose|20was|20administered-125\"> </a><code>http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK</code></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZDAK.html#IMMZDAK-Onemumpsprimaryseriesdosewasadministered-125\">One mumps primary series dose was administered-125</a></td><td>One mumps primary series dose was administered</td><td><div><p>Count of vaccines administered (where \"Vaccine type\" = \"Mumps-containing vaccines\" and \"Type of dose\" = \"Primary series\") = 1</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><a name=\"IMMZD2DTMumpsVS-http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK-The|20latest|20mumps|20dose|20was|20administered|20less|20than|204|20weeks|20ago-108\"> </a><code>http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK</code></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZDAK.html#IMMZDAK-Thelatestmumpsdosewasadministeredlessthan4weeksago-108\">The latest mumps dose was administered less than 4 weeks ago-108</a></td><td>The latest mumps dose was administered less than 4 weeks ago</td><td><div><p>Today's date − \"Date and time of vaccination\" (where \"Vaccine type\" = \"Mumps-containing vaccines\") &lt; 4 weeks</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><a name=\"IMMZD2DTMumpsVS-http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK-The|20latest|20mumps|20dose|20was|20administered|20more|20than|204|20weeks|20ago-108\"> </a><code>http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK</code></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZDAK.h